name: __EPhysicalMaterialSoftCollisionMode
doc:
Soft collision mode for a physical material.

NOTE: Must match EChaosPhysicsMaterialSoftCollisionMode

RelativeThickness: SoftCollisionThickess is a fraction of the bounds (minimum axis). Should be less than 0.5
AbsoluteThickess: SoftCollisionThickess is an absolute value in cm
